OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FLauren Price survived the toughest
OL,8,Ftest of her professional career to
OL,9,Fretain her three welterweight world
OL,10,Ftitles with a unanimous points victory
OL,11,Fover Stephanie Pineiro.
OL,13,FPrice held on to her WBA, WBC and IBF
OL,14,Fbelts by comfortable margins of 98-92,
OL,15,F98-92, 99-91 on the three judges'
OL,16,Fscorecards, but the 31-year-old was a
OL,17,Fbloody mess by the end of the 10-round
OL,18,Fcontest in Cardiff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
