OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe unbeaten Welsh fighter suffered a
OL,8,Fnasty mouth injury with blood dripping
OL,9,Fheavily from it from the fifth round,
OL,10,FPrice claiming at the end of the
OL,11,Fcontest that her lip was cut by a
OL,12,Fclash of heads.
OL,14,FPineiro is known as 'The Medicine' but
OL,15,FPrice ` who had arguably not lost a
OL,16,Fround in her nine-fight professional
OL,17,Fcareer ` dug deep in her biggest
OL,18,Fexamination to keep her belts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
