OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FFour-weight world champion Claressa
OL,8,FShields was ringside with the American
OL,9,Fin talks to meet Price either later
OL,10,Fthis year or in early 2027.
OL,12,FPrice was back on Welsh soil for the
OL,13,Ffirst time since winning her maiden
OL,14,Fworld title against Jessica McCaskill
OL,15,Fin May 2024.
OL,17,FBoxing politics had kept Price of the
OL,18,Fring for over a year after her
OL,19,Fcomfortable points victory over
OL,20,FNatasha Jonas at the Royal Albert Hall.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
