OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FWales' first female world champion
OL,8,Fsaid she could have returned to the
OL,9,Fgrand scene of that all-British
OL,10,Faffair, but her desire was to put on
OL,11,Fbig shows in her homeland.
OL,13,FPrice had warned Pineiro would be
OL,14,Fstepping into the Dragons' Den ` a
OL,15,Fpoint underlined as the Tokyo Olympic
OL,16,Fgold medallist made her entrance to
OL,17,FDafydd Iwan's Welsh anthem 'Yma O Hyd'
OL,18,Fand a crescendo of noise at the
OL,19,FUtilita Arena.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
