FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FBut southpaw Pineiro ` unbeaten in 10
OL,8,Ffights and Price's WBA mandatory
OL,9,Fchallenger ` was determined to join
OL,10,Fthe pantheon of Puerto Rican boxing
OL,11,Fgreats which include Miguel Cotto,
OL,12,FTito Trinidad, Ivan Calderon and
OL,13,FAmanda Serrano.
OL,15,FBoth boxers were patient in the
OL,16,Fopening round with Price keen to work
OL,17,Fbehind a strong jab and Pineiro also
OL,18,Fsettling in to her rhythm.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FPrice showed flashes of her speed in
OL,8,Fthe second stanza with accurate two
OL,9,Fand three-punch combinations and
OL,10,FPineiro stumbled after taking a
OL,11,Fstraight right at the end of the third.
OL,13,FPineiro was not slow to come forward
OL,14,Fbut Price was far quicker to the
OL,15,Fpunch, leaving a bruise under the
OL,16,FPuerto Rican's left eye.
OL,18,FThere was concern for Price in the
OL,19,Ffifth as blood poured from her gaping
OL,20,Fmouth, offering Pineiro real hope of
OL,21,Fcreating an upset.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775426988
OL,3,CLauren Price comes through toughest
OL,4,Cbattle yet to retain world titles in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FThe damage appeared to stir Price into
OL,8,Ffurious action in the sixth, but her
OL,9,Fall-white outfit was splattered in
OL,10,Fblood by the end of the seventh.
OL,12,FPineiro was clearly fancying her
OL,13,Fchances but Price continued to move
OL,14,Fwell and throw good shots.
OL,16,FDespite Price's damaged appearance,
OL,17,Fthe outcome was not in doubt.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
